mixin flex-container()
    section.flex-container
        div.flex-container__content.content
            h1.flex-container__title <span class='flex-container__span'>Комплексные</span>&nbspпредложения для мостостроения
            div.flex-container__title-container
            div.content__row.row.row_big
                div.row__block.content__block_grey
                    h2.row__title.content__title_blue Мостовая сталь/Стальные конструкции мостов
                    div.content__arrow-container
                        button.content__btn
                            a(href='#')
                                img.content__arrow_blue(src='../assets/images/arrow-blue.png')
                div.row__block.row__block_nested
                    div.row__nested-block.content__block_grey
                        h2.row__title.content__title_blue Железобетонные конструкции мостов
                        div.content__arrow-container
                            button.content__btn
                                a(href='#')
                                    img.content__arrow_blue(src='../assets/images/arrow-blue.png')
                    div.row__nested-block.content__block_grey
                        h2.row__title.content__title_blue Дорожные ограждения барьерного типа
                        div.content__arrow-container
                            button.content__btn
                                a(href='#')
                                    img.content__arrow_blue(src='../assets/images/arrow-blue.png')
            div.content__row.row.row_md
                div.row__block.content__block_dark-blue
                    h2.row__title.content__title_white Шпунтовой замок
                    div.content__arrow-container
                        button.content__btn
                            a(href='#')                            
                                img.content__arrow_blue(src='../assets/images/arrow-white.png')
                div.row__block.content__block_grey 
                    h2.row__title.content__title_blue Мостовой крепеж
                    div.content__arrow-container
                            button.content__btn
                                a(href='#')
                                    img.content__arrow_blue(src='../assets/images/arrow-blue.png')
                div.row__block.content__block_light-blue 
                    h2.row__title.content__title_white Профили для деформационных швов
                    div.content__arrow-container
                        button.content__btn
                            a(href='#')
                                img.content__arrow_blue(src='../assets/images/arrow-white.png')
            div.content__row.row.row_small
                div.row__block.content__block_grey
                    h2.row__title.content__title_blue Плетеные габионы
                    div.content__arrow-container
                        button.content__btn                            
                            a(href='#')
                                img.content__arrow_blue(src='../assets/images/arrow-blue.png')
                div.row__block.content__block_grey
                    h2.row__title.content__title_blue Модульные мосты
                    div.content__arrow-container
                        button.content__btn
                            a(href='#')
                                img.content__arrow_blue(src='../assets/images/arrow-blue.png')